$ Power BI Desktop

*Power BI Desktop* is an application that is locally installed on a computer and is used to connect to, transform and → development/Data/visualization[visualize data]. 

sa:
  → Microsoft/products/Power/BI

  → Microsoft/Power-Query/Editor


links:
  Power BI Desktop is free and can be downloaded from → https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=58494[here].
  -
  By default, the 64-bit version of Power BI Desktop installs under
  → Windows/dirs/Program-Files/Microsoft-Power-BI-Desktop[`C:\Program Files\Microsoft Power BI Desktop`].
